---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="404｜朴散的思想仓库">
  <article class="reading">
    <header class="reading-header">
      <div class="reading-record"><span>404</span><span>档案未找到</span></div>
      <h1>这一页还没有被公开。</h1>
      <p class="reading-deck">可能是链接写错了，也可能是这篇档案仍留在本地知识库里。</p>
    </header>
    <div class="prose">
      <p><a href={import.meta.env.BASE_URL}>返回首页</a>，或去 <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}articles/`}>文章目录</a> 继续找。</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
